{"tid":2251692,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"空姐不是你想干就能幹的","createTime":"2020-10-21T03:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T06:38:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb9e933e929d982e7b523db4ac44c8c9b46c50b","tid":2251692,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nw91ddp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnw91ddp.jpg&h=c0c869d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛向藍天是這些姑娘們的夢想，但要實現夢想，她們就得經歷一系列的魔鬼訓練。圖：無論何時何地，精緻的妝容都要保持好。<br />\n<br />\n嚴格訓練每一個站姿。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姿勢要精確到手勢細節。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n咬筷子是練習微笑的必經階段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n頭頂書是每天都會練習的內容。"},{"pid":"55201a7ee6eec40094bf366f765ddcb6834d401e","tid":2251692,"uid":366655,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"領導先幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc00d6a6e6f17ffb03b3da66ed22bf4c49822c2","tid":2251692,"uid":249347,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:35:46.000Z","msg":"空姐不是你想干就能幹的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7595e2e205d449b99848595083ac4e61e4f7c3b1","tid":2251692,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:38:27.000Z","msg":"要先脫褲子的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85c92677913098fa2e043669b61b9382ec7e2e6","tid":2251692,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZiJrBN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZiJrBN.png&h=078df168&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8554d3bf9dc4bbb9aa7e9cee0bfc14d8c113c8f0","tid":2251692,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c65a49a5503